<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR2a0007-zh-93532600" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>二十四史全譯3 漢書</title><editor role="translator">Xu Jialu 许嘉璐編</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="4">The copyright status of this work is unclear</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>二十四史全譯3 漢書</title>上海：漢語大詞典出版社，2004</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#KR2a0007"><title xml:lang="och">漢書</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="zh">Chinese</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2024-04-01T21:51:54.416+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="KR2a0007-start"><seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_072-4a.53" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-01T21:59:09.871+09:00"/><seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-7a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-01T22:01:29.023+09:00">有幸遇上赦免的命令，</seg><seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_070-7a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-01T22:01:54.619+09:00">或者那時可以免罪。</seg><seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_053-18a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-02T23:00:43.375+09:00">《春秋》記載日食三十六次，</seg><seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_053-18a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-02T23:00:58.406+09:00">地虛五次，</seg><seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_053-18a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-02T23:01:05.705+09:00">或者有夷狄侵擾中原，</seg><seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_053-18a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-02T23:01:10.348+09:00">或者大權在臣下，</seg><seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_053-18a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-02T23:01:17.898+09:00">或者有婦凌駕夫，</seg><seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_053-18a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-02T23:01:39.546+09:00">或者是臣子背叛君父，</seg><seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_053-18a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-02T23:01:47.071+09:00">事雖不同，</seg><seg corresp="#KR2a0007_tls_053-18a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-04-02T23:01:59.102+09:00">其類相同。</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>